            <lg xml:id="TK48">
<l>āṟṟi ṉoḻukki yaṟaṉiḻukkā vilvāḻkkai</l>
<l>nōṟpāri ṉōṉmai yuṭaittu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Setting others on their path without letting dharma slip, household life</l>
<l>takes more endurance than the life of endurers.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
